data.description: Welcome home to this spacious gem! Boasting over 2,000+ square feet, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom beauty on a double lot. The oversized detached garage is a perfect workshop space for all your projects.  Come inside to discover over $30K of upgrades to include brand-new kitchen that's a chef's delight, w/all new appliances, new paint, carpet & LVP. The primary bedroom features a charming balcony, providing a private retreat for you to unwind. Primary bedroom, it's incredibly spacious. Home is perfect balance between central convenience & a peaceful escape from city life. Near interstates, beaches, shopping, entertainment, and military bases.  *Ask about the 2.375% VA Assumable loan for VA eligible buyers*. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your forever home.
